You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off the fireplace.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your devices - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show.
After connecting Alexa to your Dynasty Fireplaces products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Dynasty Fireplaces" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Dynasty Fireplaces account in our "Dynasty Fireplaces" app;
(3). You need to have some Dynasty Fireplaces devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Dynasty Fireplaces" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Dynasty Fireplaces" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Dynasty Fireplaces" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Dynasty Fireplaces", and you'll be navigated to Dynasty Fireplaces login page;
(9). Input your Dynasty Fireplaces account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the fireplace.”
“Alexa,turn off the fireplace.”
“Alexa,set fireplace to 50 degrees”
"Alexa,decrease fireplace"
"Alexa,increase fireplace"
“Alexa,turn on eco on the fireplace”
“Alexa,turn on child lock on the fireplace”
“Alexa,turn on oscillate on the fireplace”
“Alexa,turn on light on the fireplace”

If you encounter issues when using this Skill, please email us at: support@dynastyfireplace.com
